"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        QueryRequestPayload structures with different query functions fields.
        """
a = payloads.QueryRequestPayload(query_functions=[enums.QueryFunction.
    QUERY_OPERATIONS, enums.QueryFunction.QUERY_OBJECTS])
b = payloads.QueryRequestPayload(query_functions=[enums.QueryFunction.
    QUERY_OBJECTS, enums.QueryFunction.QUERY_OPERATIONS])
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
